trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Data.Entity.Design.EntityClassGenerator.OnTypeGenerated"></xref> event.

trans-unit.source: The collection is empty if no attributes will be added to the type.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref href="System.Data.Objects.DataClasses.EntityObject"></xref>, <xref href="System.Data.Objects.DataClasses.ComplexObject"></xref>, or <xref href="System.Data.Objects.ObjectContext"></xref>, depending on the <xref:System.Data.Entity.Design.TypeGeneratedEventArgs.TypeSource*> property value.
